            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Although this feature has been fixed, for stable version users waiting for the 0.12.1 update, a workaround is to use commands like `<C-e>` to move the first line of the buffer out of the visible area; this will prevent the bug from being triggered. Additionally, this bug will not be triggered in files where the first line does not have a codelens.",
